1... 2... 3...

305
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:51,472
4... 5...

306
00:26:55,771 --> 00:26:59,400
La premiere règle du business,
c'est savoir à qui parler.

307
00:26:59,675 --> 00:27:02,000
Audrey!

308
